<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100..900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>Password Reset Successful</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      * {
        padding: 0 !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
      }

      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        height: fit-content !important;
      }

      p {
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .body {
        width: 680px !important;
        margin: 0 auto !important;
        padding: 51.67px 48px 75.35px !important;
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
      }

      .main_div {
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        margin: 46.76px auto 0 !important;
        width: 520px;
        max-width: 520px;
        border-radius: 16px !important;
        background-color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
      }

      .top_div {
        padding: 48px 40px !important;
      }

      .success_icon {
        width: 64px !important;
        height: 64px !important;
        margin: 0 auto 24px auto !important;
        display: block !important;
        background-color: #dcfce7;
        border-radius: 50%;
        padding: 16px !important;
      }

      .checkmark {
        width: 32px !important;
        height: 32px !important;
        stroke: #16a34a;
        stroke-width: 3;
      }

      .user_name {
        line-height: 32px !important;
        font-size: 24px !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #111827;
        margin-bottom: 24px !important;
      }

      .content_text {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        line-height: 24px !important;
        color: #4b5563;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 16px !important;
      }

      .content_text_span {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #16a34a;
      }

      .success_box {
        background-color: #f0fdf4;
        border: 1px solid #86efac;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px !important;
        margin: 24px 0 !important;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .success_title {
        font-size: 18px !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #166534;
        margin-bottom: 8px !important;
      }

      .success_text {
        font-size: 14px !important;
        color: #15803d;
        margin: 0 !important;
      }

      .alert_box {
        background-color: #fef2f2;
        border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px !important;
        margin: 24px 0 !important;
      }

      .alert_text {
        font-size: 14px !important;
        line-height: 20px !important;
        color: #991b1b;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin: 0 !important;
      }

      .security_tips {
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px !important;
        margin: 24px 0 !important;
      }

      .security_title {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #111827;
        margin-bottom: 12px !important;
      }

      .security_list {
        padding-left: 20px !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
      }

      .security_list li {
        font-size: 14px !important;
        line-height: 20px !important;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-bottom: 8px !important;
        padding-left: 0 !important;
      }

      .regard_div {
        margin: 32px 0 !important;
      }

      .regard_text {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        line-height: 24px !important;
        margin-bottom: 4px !important;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #111827;
      }

      .regard_team {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        line-height: 24px !important;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #6b7280;
      }

      .footer_div {
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        padding: 32px 40px !important;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px !important;
      }

      .footer_text {
        font-size: 14px !important;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-bottom: 8px !important;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 20px !important;
      }

      .support_link {
        color: #2563eb !important;
        font-weight: 500;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #2563eb;
      }

      @media (max-width: 769px) {
        .body {
          width: unset !important;
          padding: 32px 24px !important;
        }

        .main_div {
          width: unset !important;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 540px) {
        .top_div {
          padding: 32px 24px !important;
        }

        .user_name {
          font-size: 20px !important;
        }

        .content_text {
          font-size: 15px !important;
        }

        .footer_div {
          padding: 24px !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="body">
    <div class="main_div">
      <section class="top_div">
        <div class="success_icon">
          <svg class="checkmark" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M20 6L9 17L4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <p class="user_name">Hi {{name}},</p>

        <div class="success_box">
          <p class="success_title">Password Reset Successful!</p>
          <p class="success_text">
            Your Kochanet Chat account password has been successfully changed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="content_text">
          You can now log in to your account using your new password. All your data and conversations remain secure and unchanged.
        </p>

        <div class="alert_box">
          <p class="alert_text">
            ⚠ If you didn't make this change, please contact our support team immediately at
            <a href="mailto:support@kochanet.com" style="color: #991b1b !important; text-decoration: underline;">support@kochanet.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="security_tips">
          <p class="security_title">Security Tips:</p>
          <ul class="security_list">
            <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
            <li>Use a strong, unique password for your account</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
            <li>Regularly update your password</li>
            <li>Be cautious of phishing attempts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="content_text">
          If you have any questions or concerns about your account security, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.
        </p>

        <div class="regard_div">
          <p class="regard_text">Best regards,</p>
          <p class="regard_team">The Kochanet Team</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="footer_div">
        <p class="footer_text">
          This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.
        </p>
        <p class="footer_text">
          © {{year}} Kochanet Chat. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
